    "description": "你可能永远无法预料到自己将身处于这种境地，但还是深陷其中：你需要通过洗钱来帮助一个墨西哥犯罪集团。这个集团从不接受借口，也几乎不给试错的余地。你一定不会想让他们失望。你清楚上一个这样做的人下场如何。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724540/extras/c009232b07600dcc21768d6c3121e29d.poster.avif?t=1698061456\" width=616 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724540/extras/c009232b07600dcc21768d6c3121e29d.webm?t=1698061456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724540/extras/c009232b07600dcc21768d6c3121e29d.mp4?t=1698061456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>就这样，你将从明尼苏达州的一个僻静小镇开始，这是一个由美丽森林和黑暗秘密所萦绕的小镇。其中帮派林立，而他们决不想把自己的地盘与后起之秀共享……在这样一个孤立无援的情况下，你能存活下来吗？<br><br>你需要拿出全部的勇气、智慧与毅力来征服面前所有的挑战。尽管你最亲近的人可能会背叛你，但在一些最意想不到的地方，你可能会找到自己的盟友。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724540/extras/d64bb5288861cdc53f4a82a13f7d8f02.avif?t=1698061456\" width=599 height=90 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>计划你的行动，收购企业，守卫并扩张你的事业<br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724540/extras/a2e27e3ed5ef8a4c61b289c1a3599c6d.poster.avif?t=1698061456\" width=616 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724540/extras/a2e27e3ed5ef8a4c61b289c1a3599c6d.webm?t=1698061456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724540/extras/a2e27e3ed5ef8a4c61b289c1a3599c6d.mp4?t=1698061456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>在警察与两个当地犯罪帮派之间平衡你的声望，以免那些你没法依赖的盟友与你反目成仇<br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724540/extras/d23f977d8314b5bc33990e91840459e4.poster.avif?t=1698061456\" width=616 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724540/extras/d23f977d8314b5bc33990e91840459e4.webm?t=1698061456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724540/extras/d23f977d8314b5bc33990e91840459e4.mp4?t=1698061456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>完美的解决方案并不存在，你必须做出抉择并面对那些并非即时产生的后果<br> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724540/extras/385de2821eae08b021aeebde2b42d7df.poster.avif?t=1698061456\" width=616 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724540/extras/385de2821eae08b021aeebde2b42d7df.webm?t=1698061456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1724540/extras/385de2821eae08b021aeebde2b42d7df.mp4?t=1698061456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br></li><li>接纳黑暗，提升在集团里的地位，尝试向FBI寻求帮助……或是找其他的方式来保证你的安全与自立 </li></ul>",
